name: PJ Berri (Parappa the Rapper)
description:
PJ Berri is a character who appears in the Parappa the Rapper franchise.  He is the best friend of the main character Parappa and is known for his personality of having a big appetite and being tired all the time. 

To celebrate the 20th anniversary of the franchise PJ Berri starred in a spinoff of anime shorts titled "PJ Berri no Mogu Mogu Munya Munya"
